{"tid":1720106,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[Sony/罪大滔天]相機集中討論區 (48)","createTime":"2019-11-14T09:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:09:51.000Z","uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a5bd5bb5e5c5d27fcff81ed1ef3384d4b858428","tid":1720106,"uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新手請睇第一頁完再問<br />\n影人影景買咩鏡睇Q&amp;A</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">攝影窮三代   單（無）反毀一生<br />\n鏡坑深似海，買鏡前請衡量銀包承受力</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/07/Sony_guilty.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081211110622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F07%2FSony_guilty.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20081211110622&h=413b43c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/000744_0269b4a77c16cff50cff0481c2b16e3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F000744_0269b4a77c16cff50cff0481c2b16e3f.jpg&h=d9275000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）首先講下Sony機目前比較多人講嘅優缺點 ：<br />\n優點：機身性能好、對焦快、畫質好、價錢合理。<br />\n缺點：直出顏色唔討好、APS-C 鏡頭群略少。<br />\n<br />\n直出顏色方面其實手機調兩下，Post 社交媒體已經夠做。<br />\n真係認真執嘅話用返Lightroom／Photoshop，Sony嘅Raw檔細節保留得好好。<br />\n引述巴打講過嘅：「無話直出唔得，曝光正常構圖好設定微調過，基本上實見得人嘅。不過Sony機基本上保留細節較多，一般直出會有層「Sony灰」，所以唔太理想。但係用Lr類軟件，套Preset (e.g. VSCO)再微調就會出色好多。」<br />\n<br />\nAPS-C 鏡頭群略少，變焦方面無乜選擇，定焦鏡應有都有。<br />\n2）選購機身懶人包<br />\n1&rdquo;隨身機：<br />\n主要錄影、不需高速對焦、連拍 － Rx100 M4。<br />\n需要高速對焦 － Rx100 M5V/M6/M7。<br />\n<br />\nFull Frame 隨身機：<br />\nRx1、Rx1R、Rx1R2。<br />\n<br />\nAPS-C 無反：<br />\na6100 － 沒有了 HLG、S-Log3、S-Log2，OLED 觀景窗舊一點。<br />\na6400 － 即時追焦及眼部對焦。為A6100/A6600 基礎。<br />\na6600 － 5 輻機身防震，拍片用的即時眼部對焦系統，改用新 A7 系列用的 Z 系充電池<br />\n<br />\nFull Frame 無反：<br />\nA7iii － 基本上手感、對焦、連拍、iso、各功能都比A7ii 提升左一個層次。<br />\nA7Riii － High Resolution，Riii 比Rii 對焦快一點，用新電，但畫質上冇太大分別。<br />\nA7Riv － 更高Resolution，6100萬像素。<br />\nA9 － 旗艦。<br />\n畢直夠既話一律建議上三代 (7iii,7Riii,7Riv,9)。<br />\n<br />\nRx10 系列唔熟，有需要再留言問下其他巴打。"},{"pid":"97a4957dbf943614c950144d6a1bf884ddca7692","tid":1720106,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:00:54.000Z","msg":"之前上showroom玩過部rx0 ii<br />\n幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcbe49798c6b1235c346888ae75bb30bf3dfa7d","tid":1720106,"uid":13010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"a73 由年頭到而家都無咩跌過價"},{"pid":"69e6997340e9ec975182018ab7c3ebfef982b9a5","tid":1720106,"uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdcbe49798c6b1235c346888ae75bb30bf3dfa7d","tid":1720106,"uid":13010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"a73 由年頭到而家都無咩跌過價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"等a74 出佢就會跌"},{"pid":"cc7f6d8ac64445a10405123cfab753c82760a692","tid":1720106,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"想問下big camera 買鏡頭會唔會抵d?<br />\n同埋產地會唔會有分別？"},{"pid":"99bee99a8f8bd26c5f28b727b844d66cace7ca61","tid":1720106,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69e6997340e9ec975182018ab7c3ebfef982b9a5","tid":1720106,"uid":28461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdcbe49798c6b1235c346888ae75bb30bf3dfa7d","tid":1720106,"uid":13010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"a73 由年頭到而家都無咩跌過價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"等a74 出佢就會跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等得你錯過左幾多個moment"},{"pid":"36e2c41fe9ef570521249f7df6a375e789ce66c1","tid":1720106,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike"